g year specific responsibilities  The cadet remembers that faculty advisors will endeavor to provide all reasonable assistance for their education  but that degree completion and program monitoring are the cadet s primary responsibility  Cadets Should  Fulfill class specific Cadet Responsibilities  Contact their advisor immediately if they begin to have difficulties  Be aware that degree completion is the responsibility of the cadet  Know the role of their academic advisor Calculating GPA by hand How to Increase your GPA GPA Projection Tool for 2014   younger cadets Cadet Resources  Post View Instructions  Account Summary Financial Aid Create An Authorized Bill Payer  ROTC Requirements  Will you have what it takes to return to VMI  Guidelines for Academic Appeals  Registrar s Forms    VMI Foundation Keydet Club Alumni Webcams Directories My VMI  RESOURCES   Title IX  Health   Safety   IT   Site Index Parents   Families   Cadets   Non discrimination Statement   Privacy   THE VMI PHILOSOPHY The VMI experience is framed by relevant education within a military environment  It s an education that develops character  fosters a lifelong appreciation of physical fitness engenders a sense of responsibility to others  and cultivates the ability to master adversity  VIRGINIA MILITARY INSTITUTE Lexington  Virginia 24450 General Information   540  464 7230  Admissions  admissions vmi edu 